    At the beginning of the War of the Kinslayers, several chromatic dragons chased the dwarves of Stengrotto into the Underdark, tunnelling into
    the earth and ever after living in gem-filled caverns in the deep. Over the course of millennia, they adapted to the psionic energy emitted by
    the gemstones, and were slowly transformed in a process similar to the Edelian dwarves of Despin.
  </p>
  <p>
    Knowledge of gem dragons is scant even among scholars. As such, gem dragonborn are exceedingly rare. Unlike other dragons, they have no
